  Join multiple ranges horizontally with arrayformula syntax
  =QUERY({range1,range2},"select *")

  Pivot Table - like
  =QUERY('Data Sheet'!A1:B6;"select A, sum(B), count(B) group by A")

  select F, sum(G) where E != ‘’ group by F label ‘total retweets’
  
